08:07.237 --> 08:08.272
Oh.

08:08.405 --> 08:10.657
(Clicking fingers) One, two...

08:10.783 --> 08:12.819
Uh, uh, tell it, Jack.

08:12.951 --> 08:14.942
(Trumpet plays intro)

08:38.977 --> 08:41.764
— (Bell tinkles)
— Jingle jangle, jingle jangle.

08:41.897 --> 08:44.604
— (Music playing over speakers)
— Cha—ching!

08:44.733 --> 08:46.974
Another 60 units for you, bro.

08:47.111 --> 08:48.601
