you should come in and sign a few copies.

09:11.552 --> 09:14.134
Yeah. Hey, how about
an in—store performance,

09:14.263 --> 09:16.720
— me and my band?
- That too.

09:17.808 --> 09:19.890
— Thanks, man.
— Have a good day.

09:21.061 --> 09:24.053
Well, I might take your walk—in cooler,

09:24.189 --> 09:27.477
