09:32.865 --> 09:35.948
Spoken like a man getting ready
to open yet another restaurant.

09:36.076 --> 09:38.692
(Chuckles) It's a bad habit.

09:40.205 --> 09:42.992
So how are you feeling? You all right?

09:43.125 --> 09:44.535
(Sighs)

09:44.668 --> 09:47.831
To be honest,
the stress was making my hair fall out.

09:47.963 --> 09:49.624
| just want to catch my breath.

09:49.757 --> 09:51.622
You gonna stay here in New Orleans?

09:51.759 --> 09:54.375
Believe it or not, my SBA loan check
finally came through.

09:54.511 --> 09:56.422
Too little, too late for the restaurant,

09:56.555 --> 09:59.092
