09:59.224 --> 10:01.681
with a two—burner, grill, smoker.

10:01.810 --> 10:03.425
No shit.

10:03.562 --> 10:05.473
Do the guerrilla—chef thing for a while.

10:05.606 --> 10:08.348
No overhead, no reservations,
no fucking mortgage.

10:08.484 --> 10:10.520
