14:12.102 --> 14:14.514
most of it undamaged by the storm,

14:14.646 --> 14:16.432
when people can't get home.

14:16.565 --> 14:20.228
— Are you hoping to be arrested?
- (Siren approaching)

14:20.360 --> 14:22.817
— I expect to be.
— (Man) Here they come!

14:22.946 --> 14:25.653
