take a charge, understand?

14:49.639 --> 14:51.846
— Yes, sir.
— (Man) Get me a wide shot.

14:51.975 --> 14:53.431
— You got that?
— All of it.

14:53.560 --> 14:55.596
— Are we rolling?
- (Banging)

14:56.480 --> 14:57.515
Sir?

14:57.647 --> 15:00.810
