45:16.214 --> 45:19.251
deciding which neighborhoods
they think ought to go back

45:21.595 --> 45:24.052
And, oh yeah, while no one was looking,

45:24.180 --> 45:27.343
they just laid off every single schoolteacher
in Orleans Parish

45:27.475 --> 45:32.390
because no one's plans apparently
included the public school system.

45:36.943 --> 45:40.310
So, America, if you're feeling guilty

45:40.447 --> 45:42.278
for your Katrina fatigue,

45:42.407 --> 45:45.240
I'm here to put things into perspective.

45:45.368 --> 45:47.404
It's not all about you.

45:47.537 --> 45:49.368
Really.

45:49.497 --> 45:53.115
Because down here in the city of misrule,

45:53.251 --> 45:56.994
we are, always...

45:57.130 --> 45:59.212
our own worst enemy.

